<li>Thinking of you and sending all my love during this painful time.</li>
<li>I'll always cherish the memories we shared with [deceased's name].</li>
<li>My heart aches for you; please know I'm here for whatever you need.</li>
<li>You're in my thoughts and prayers; may you find peace in the days ahead.</li>
<li>I'm so incredibly sorry for your loss.  [deceased's name] will be deeply missed.</li>
<li> Sending you strength and comfort; may your memories of [deceased's name] bring you solace.</li>
<li> Know that I'm here for you; your friendship means so much to me.</li>
<li> I'll always remember [deceased's name]'s [positive quality]. They will be missed by all.</li>
<li> My deepest sympathy; may fond memories bring you comfort and peace.</li>
<li> It was a privilege to know [deceased's name]. They will be truly missed.</li>
<li> Your friendship means the world to me, and I'm here for you through this.</li>
<li> I'm so sorry to hear about the passing of your friend; my heart goes out to you.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and remembering all the good times we shared with [deceased's name].</li>
<li> Please accept my heartfelt condolences; I’m here if you need anything, big or small.</li>
    

